OL,3,CDrug driver who killed 16-year-old
OL,4,Cmoped rider jailed
OL,6,FA drug driver has been sentenced to
OL,7,Ffive years in prison for causing the
OL,8,Fdeath of a teenager in South
OL,9,FGloucestershire.
OL,11,FHarry Charlton, 29, pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fcausing the death of 16-year-old
OL,13,FDaniel Davies by careless driving
OL,14,Fwhile over the prescribed limit of
OL,15,Fdrugs.
OL,17,FThe crash happened on the A4174
OL,18,FWraxall Road roundabout on 17 April
OL,19,F2022.
