OL,3,CDrug driver who killed 16-year-old
OL,4,Cmoped rider jailed
OL,6,FThe court heard how he drove through a
OL,7,Fred light at the through-about
OL,8,Fjunction near Warmley and hit Daniel,
OL,9,Fwho was driving his moped.
OL,11,FWhen he was tested, Charlton was found
OL,12,Fto be just over the legal limit for
OL,13,Fcannabis.
OL,15,FDaniel died at the scene after
OL,16,Fsuffering a head injury. He had
OL,17,Frecently celebrated his 16th birthday
OL,18,Fon 1 March.
