OL,3,CDrug driver who killed 16-year-old
OL,4,Cmoped rider jailed
OL,6,FThe teenager was due to start an
OL,7,Fapprenticeship and had only had the
OL,8,Fmoped for four days when the collision
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,FLast year, dozens of bikers took to
OL,12,Fthe streets to remember him.
OL,14,FHarry Charlton was sentenced to five
OL,15,Fyears in prison. He was also given a
OL,16,Ftwo year driving ban and will have to
OL,17,Ftake an extended driving test after
OL,18,Fthat.
