OL,6,FHis honour Judge Picton said on
OL,7,Fsentencing: "Sentencing, Judge Martin
OL,8,FPicton said: "Daniel Davies was 16
OL,9,Fwhen he died, tragically and
OL,10,Funnecessarily. He had his whole life
OL,11,Fin front of him.
OL,13,F"You, Harry Charlton drove through a
OL,14,Fred light with cannabis above the
OL,15,Flimit for driving.
OL,17,F"Your level of concentration was
OL,18,Faffected by the cannabis as was your
OL,19,Fability to safely control your
OL,20,Fvehicle. You should have stopped at
OL,21,Fthe red light."
