OL,6,FDaniel's mum, Sam Davies, has paid the
OL,7,Ffollowing tribute to her son,
OL,8,Ffollowing today's sentencing:
OL,10,F"I will never understand why Daniel
OL,11,Fwas taken from us so soon and there
OL,12,Fwill never be a sentence long enough.
OL,14,F"He was one of the 'good ones' in
OL,15,Flife. He was clever, funny and had a
OL,16,Fgood heart. He had his whole future
OL,17,Fahead of him.
OL,19,F"The pain of losing Daniel is a pain
OL,20,Flike no other, a sadness sadder than
OL,21,Fany sad.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
