OL,6,F"Myself, the family, friends and his
OL,7,Ffriends will miss him forever but we
OL,8,Fwill all live for him and never forget
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,F"Daniel we are, in your words for your
OL,12,Fdad, 'living for you' and we always
OL,13,Fwill. I love you Dan x"
OL,15,FInvestigating officer Dai Nicholas
OL,16,Fsaid: "Daniel's family have shown
OL,17,Fextraordinary courage over an
OL,18,Funimaginably difficult two-and-a-half-
OL,19,Fyears and I'd like to pay tribute to
OL,20,Fthem for that.
