OL,4,Cmoped rider jailed
OL,6,F"This is yet another example of
OL,7,Fsomeone's life being tragically cut
OL,8,Fshort due to a driver not being in a
OL,9,Ffit state to be on the roads.
OL,11,F"Drugs impair your ability to drive
OL,12,Fsafely and risk causing yourself or
OL,13,Fother motorists coming to serious harm.
OL,15,F"Charlton was solely responsible for
OL,16,FDaniel's death and will face the
OL,17,Fconsequences of his decisions that
OL,18,Fnight for the rest of his life."
